content.metadata: Open a web browser and navigate to the OrangeHRM login page by entering 'https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com/web/index.php/auth/login' in the address bar.
On the OrangeHRM login page, locate the 'Username' input field and click on it. Then, enter 'admin' into the Username field.
